<plot>Camino a la Victoria is a docudrama/narrative about the tragedies that an immigrant has to go through in the borders of Mexico and the United States. Through the eyes of Cheko Carrivano, a story is told of immigrants that had to go through rape in an immigrant house, bloody violence due to money, and dead inside a moving truck due to the heat and humidity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?091702</url></doc>
